          Prosthetics design
          Prosthetics are always improving, especially lower limb
          prosthetics, as restoring ambulation is one of the most
          important processes in physical rehabilitation. Despite
          improvements in lower limb prosthetics, upper limb prosthetics
          have been left behind, still using simplistic pylley
          systems.
          
          
          Education
          BSc | Prosthetics and Orthotics
          University of Strathclyde | 2017-Currently
          High School | Julius Janonis Gymnasium
          2013-2017, Siauliai, Lithuania
          
          
          Work experience
          UNO Parks | Instructor | Summer of
          2018
          Farm Worker | My dad’s farm for the last 4
          years.
